Dialogue: 0,0:22:19.73,0:22:23.66,EDCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\bord0\c&HFFF7FB&\shad2\pos(317,462)}一点小事也要争吵
Dialogue: 0,0:22:23.66,0:22:29.66,EDCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\bord0\c&HFFF7FB&\shad2\pos(317,462)}会不会有一天我们再也不能见面
Dialogue: 0,0:22:30.37,0:22:35.00,EDCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\bord0\c&HFFF7FB&\shad2\pos(317,462)}不知道
